# VibeCraft — Fighter 3-D Model (Wavefront OBJ)
#
# Fantasy warrior in a dynamic battle-ready pose: sword raised,
# weight shifted, flowing cape. More heroic proportions with
# detailed armor pieces for that classic RPG aesthetic.
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.1 units tall, centred at origin
# Poly count  : ~180 triangles
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Parts:
#   Head        — knight's great helm with visor and plume
#   Torso       — breastplate with flared pauldrons
#   Cape        — flowing cloak attached at shoulders
#   Waist       — armored tasset/belt
#   Left Arm    — pauldron + upper arm + vambrace + gauntlet + heater shield
#   Right Arm   — pauldron + upper arm + vambrace + gauntlet + raised sword
#   Left Leg    — cuisses + greave + sabatons
#   Right Leg   — cuisses + greave + sabatons (weight-bearing, slightly forward)

